description: The path slopes steeply downhill to the north, and up to the high ground in the southwest.  High overhead you can hear the cry of a solitary hawk, probably out hunting up a meal.
The path slopes steeply downhill to the north, and up to the high ground in the southwest.  High overhead stretches a vault of stars, parts blotted out by the occasional cloud.
title: [Lysierian Hills, Forest Path]
